      "content": "idk, it just feels like a lot of unnecessary worry for just a little bit of wine. my friend said people only really get sick if they drink a lot of it. if i just stick to one small glass i'll probably be totally fine and won't even notice anything, right? i really dont want to deal with a doctor over a glass of wine.",
